data.description: Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a great home in a great location! This cozy 3 bedroom, 1 bath home is located close to schools, and close to downtown Manteno. The finished basement would be a great extra space for anything you need, playspace, crafting area, or extra living space. Come summertime, you will love your backyard oasis with an inground pool, deck, and screened in porch. Property is being sold "As-Is" and is ready for someone new to love it!
